		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Stephen Elliott</span></strong> is the author of two books, <em>Jones Inn</em> (Boneyard Press) and <em>Don&rsquo;t Make Me Hate You </em>(iUniverse). He left home at thirteen and has worked as a stripper, a cabdriver, a bartender, and a marketing executive. He avoids small children and long-term relationships. He lives in San Francisco.</p><a href="/contributors/stephen-elliott" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
